02:00.486 --> 02:03.603
He makes you look his baseball cards and tell him they're good.

02:03.617 --> 02:05.423
They're not good.

02:05.427 --> 02:06.592
I don't like him.

02:06.595 --> 02:09.043
I'll bet Nelson won't even have gift bags.

02:09.044 --> 02:11.213
Unthinkable!
Is that legal?

02:11.215 --> 02:14.231
