06:55.998 --> 06:57.491
Bart, where you going?

06:57.505 --> 06:58.963
I saved you a seat,

06:59.148 --> 07:00.542
best friend.

07:00.557 --> 07:01.131
Wouha!

07:02.117 --> 07:03.450
Ha-ha!

07:05.825 --> 07:07.051
Hey, best friend,

07:07.058 --> 07:08.530
I got you a present.

07:08.547 --> 07:10.932
An entire case of pool cue chalk.

07:11.127 --> 07:12.101
Huh? Huh?

07:12.337 --> 07:15.003
We can make the tip
of anything blue.

07:15.005 --> 07:16.550
Um, Nelson,

07:16.556 --> 07:19.651
I was just thinking about us being best friends.

07:19.657 --> 07:21.601
Whoa! Me, too!

07:21.605 --> 07:23.632
We are so connected!

07:23.817 --> 07:24.902
Look, um,

07:24.975 --> 07:28.262
I don't have time for new friends.

07:28.325 --> 07:29.660
I got a lot on my plate.

07:29.666 --> 07:30.841
I've got a big report due

07:30.858 --> 07:32.481
on the Nile River topic sentence,

07:32.488 --> 07:34.212
bibliography, page numbers

07:34.226 --> 07:35.011
it's nuts.

07:35.857 --> 07:36.920
Dude...

07:37.028 --> 07:39.943
You made me get water on my cheek.

07:44.685 --> 07:46.600
Bart is my best friend now,

07:46.608 --> 07:49.740
which means no one picks on him ever again.

07:51.287 --> 07:52.612
Okay! Okay!

07:52.615 --> 07:54.940
I forgot how cool Bart was.

07:55.368 --> 07:56.280
Yeah, he's awesome.

07:56.286 --> 07:57.261
Good guy, good guy.

07:57.267 --> 07:57.901
Isn't he?

07:57.935 --> 08:00.650
I've known him for years, but I ran into him at a party

08:00.656 --> 08:01.973
and we really clicked.

08:01.986 --> 08:03.943
That's right, we're best friends now.

08:03.946 --> 08:05.802
So why don't you go pick on

08:05.806 --> 08:08.010
