08:12.437 --> 08:14.630
Yeah, we'll jump 'em while they're napping.

08:16.608 --> 08:17.543
Homie...

08:18.697 --> 08:19.142
Huh...?

08:21.245 --> 08:24.061
When you're done putting Lisa to bed we can, uh...

08:24.165 --> 08:26.823
finish what we started the other day.

08:26.827 --> 08:27.490
Woo-hoo!

08:27.496 --> 08:28.890
Marital sex!

08:29.037 --> 08:29.751
Hi hi hi

08:29.878 --> 08:32.232
Okay, tucked in tight, glass of water,

08:32.236 --> 08:33.972
nightlight on, no barn owls,

08:33.988 --> 08:35.621
don't do drugs, love you, good night.

08:36.255 --> 08:38.821
Dad, can't you read me a story for a little bit?

08:38.826 --> 08:41.683
But your mother smells like coconut.

08:44.027 --> 08:46.440
Okay, sweetie, which book should I read?

08:46.665 --> 08:49.840
Angelica Button and the Dragon King's Trundle Bed.

08:49.845 --> 08:51.070
It's the ninth book in

08:51.075 --> 08:52.551
