to Mount Purgatorium.

09:41.207 --> 09:43.612
Oh, Dad, I'm tired.

09:43.675 --> 09:45.853
- We read more tomorrow.
- Tomorrow?

09:46.058 --> 09:47.303
But she's in trouble now.

09:47.355 --> 09:49.151
I'll just read ahead
without you.

09:49.258 --> 09:52.480
No! We have to read it together.

09:52.537 --> 09:55.253
Oh, of course.
Whatever you say, sweetie.

09:55.267 --> 09:56.251
Nighty-night.

10:08.407 --> 10:11.650
