wish you weren't a bully?

10:17.607 --> 10:19.201
Mm, sometimes.

10:19.256 --> 10:22.052
But it's not up to me,
it's who I am.

10:22.107 --> 10:25.653
I mean, a shark can't stop
swimming or it'll blow up.

10:25.955 --> 10:28.953
Man...
I never knew you were so deep.

10:28.955 --> 10:31.101
