no, no, no, to me... </i>

11:24.256 --> 11:27.663
So, Scoty, how do you like school?

11:27.765 --> 11:28.661
Closed!

11:31.337 --> 11:33.292
Life was perfect.

11:34.308 --> 11:37.191
Lisa, I'm home.
Time for me to read to you!

11:37.295 --> 11:39.253
Lisa's sleeping
over at Janey's.

11:39.458 --> 11:42.703
Apparently, her mom makes
good mac and cheese.

11:44.555 --> 11:47.902
Homer? Homer.

11:48.658 --> 11:49.880
You must read ahead.

11:49.988 --> 11:51.103
Fiction is your passion!

11:51.105 --> 11:53.972
Lady, you're nice,
but I'm married.

11:53.977 --> 11:56.560
Just read the book, you shaved ape.

11:57.507 --> 12:01.500
