12:11.207 --> 12:15.102
- We hooked him, Galahad.
-Yes, quite.

12:15.407 --> 12:19.603
"Angelica was trapped in the
suffoclock of Sandy Doom..."

12:22.008 --> 12:24.900
"...as Headmaster Greystash
fought a battle to the finish

12:24.957 --> 12:28.120
with dark wizard Maluicious Krubb."

12:28.227 --> 12:29.802
