13:09.485 --> 13:11.333
- Yo, bully.
- What up, my bully?

13:12.757 --> 13:14.400
How come they can say it?

13:15.485 --> 13:16.613
They just can, okay?

13:16.688 --> 13:19.782
It's weird to see you
as somebody's sidekick.

13:19.988 --> 13:22.523
Whoa, Bart Simpson is nobody's sidekick.

13:22.585 --> 13:24.603
Then why are you wearing that vest?

13:24.908 --> 13:27.780
Because my chest is cold
and my arms aren't.

13:27.986 --> 13:28.982
I see.

13:28.987 --> 13:32.673
Then i'm suppose you can just
fly kites with whoever you want,

13:32.677 --> 13:35.051
