14:02.536 --> 14:04.232
I was waiting
to smash this frog with you,

14:04.236 --> 14:05.351
and it peed in my hand.

14:08.305 --> 14:09.783
Sorry. I was, uh...

14:09.805 --> 14:12.780
- Steal a loose grapeshe grocery store.
- Really?

14:13.085 --> 14:15.862
