14:20.807 --> 14:23.152
We were just having fun.
Don't get upset.

14:23.198 --> 14:25.953
Oh, right. Stupid Nelson always gets upset.

14:26.055 --> 14:27.602
He'll probably do something stupid.

14:27.656 --> 14:29.251
like smash his own camera!

14:31.906 --> 14:33.080
Look what you made me do!

14:35.175 --> 14:36.871
Nelson, get in here!

14:36.956 --> 14:40.043
